   Glassy-Winged Sharpshooter Glassy-Winged Sharpshooter
   New to California, threatens to spread the destructive Pierce's Disease
   Bacterium to grapes and other important crops throughout the state. A
   multi-tiered effort is underway to successfully counter this harmful
   pest.
